GSE64810_series_matrix.txt.gz.title: C_0002
GSE64810_series_matrix.txt.gz.extract_pr: QIAzol, Qiagen miRNeasy kit
Illumina TruSeq RNA Sample Prep Kit, mRNA
GSE64810_series_matrix.txt.gz.data_proce: Bases were called with the Illumina CASAVA 1.7 pipeline

mRNA-Seq reads were aligned against UCSC hg19 genome build with tophat 2.0.1, parameters --read-mismatches=3 --read-edit-dist=3 --max-multihits=20 --splice-mismatches=1 --microexon-search --coverage-search --mate-inner-dist=50 --mate-std-dev=50 –num-threads=8
Aligned reads were counted against the Gencode v17 gene annotation using htseq-count in the HTSeq package with –mode=intersection-nonempty
Genes were filtered from further analysis that had more than half of both HD and Control samples with zero counts
Outlier sample counts in individual genes were filtered
Differential expression between HD and Control was assessed using DESeq2 v1.3.34
Genome_build: hg19
Supplementary_files_format_and_content: processed files contain normalized counts for all samples and differential expression values from DESeq2, in tab delimited format
